title: Cardi B., Bodak Yellow, That's My Jam, Future Wife, Boss and Dreams, Old Music, New Music, Are You Smarter Than Tommy, Faith VS Tommy, 1 Million Dollars, Closing Remarks and more.
itunes:title: Cardi B., Bodak Yellow, That's My Jam, Future Wife, Boss and Dreams, Old Music, New Music, Are You Smarter Than Tommy, Faith VS Tommy, 1 Million Dollars, Closing Remarks and more.
description:
Happy Friday! Steve and the crew are in rare form today. The King and Fool #2 are singing their favorite songs. Throwback tracks that take you way back giving you flashbacks. What are the qualities of Miss Right? Find out how good of a boss The CEO really is according to the crew. Are You Smarter Than Tommy? Faith VS Tommy. Do you remember cassette tapes and recording off of the radio? What about downloads and streaming services. We compare the way music is given to us yesterday and today. Want to know how to make $1,000,000? Closing Remarks has the answer plus much more!
